    line-height: 1.6;">(In the clubroom…)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “Does anybody else notice somebody’s absent?”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Natsuki: “I’m…not sure WHO you’re talking about, Monika.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Yuri: “Well, Monika, could you be a little more specific? Are you referring to someone in particular?”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “Hmm, well, I haven’t seen Sayori today. She’s usually one of the first ones to arrive.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Natsuki: “Oh, now that you mention it, I haven’t seen her either. I hope she’s okay.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Yuri: “Perhaps we should try giving her a call to check on her well-being?”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “That’s a good idea, Yuri. Let me try contacting her.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;(Monika takes out her phone and dials Sayori’s number.)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “Hmm, no answer. That’s unusual. Sayori always has her phone with her.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Natsuki: “Maybe she forgot to charge it again. That happens sometimes.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;(Meanwhile, at Sayori’s place…)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Sayori: (rubbing her baby bump, feeling her unborn daughter kick) “There, there, little Sky. It won’t be long now until you join me and my friends.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;(Sayori’s phone starts ringing.)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Sayori: (startled) “Oh! My phone! Who could be calling me at this hour?”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;(Sayori picks up the phone and sees Monika’s name on the screen.)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Sayori: “Monika? Isn’t it club time already? I’m sorry I’m not there, I overslept!”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “Sayori, we were worried about you! Is everything alright?”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Sayori: (smiling) “Everything’s fine, Monika. I was just feeling baby Sky kicking. I promise I’ll be there soon.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “Oh, that’s a relief, Sayori. We were getting worried. Take your time, and make sure you take care of yourself. We can start the club meeting a bit later.&quot;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Sayori: “Thank you, Monika. I’ll be there as soon as I can. Please let the others know.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “Of course, Sayori. See you soon!”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;(Sayori hangs up and quickly gets ready. She makes her way to the clubroom, where Monika, Natsuki, and Yuri are waiting.)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Sayori: “Sorry for making you all worry. I’m here now.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Natsuki: “Geez, Sayori, you scared us. Don’t do that again!”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Yuri: “We’re just glad you’re okay, Sayori.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Monika: “Yes, Sayori, your health is the most important thing. We’re happy to have you here.”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Sayori: “Thank you, everyone. I’ll make sure to take better care of myself from now on. Anyways…” (lifting up her outfit to reveal her baby bump) “…does anyone want to feel little Sky kicking?”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;(Natsuki notices little Sky’s movements in Sayori’s womb.)</div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
    background-color: #fff3e6;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    line-height: 1.6;"><p>Natsuki: "Wow, that's amazing! I've never felt a baby kick before. Can I...can I feel?"</p>
<p>Sayori: "Of course, Natsuki!"</p>
<p>(Sayori takes Natsuki's hand and gently places it on her baby bump.)</p>
<p>Natsuki: (feeling the kicks) "Oh my gosh, it's amazing! They're so strong!"</p>
<p>Yuri: "May I have a turn as well, Sayori?"</p>
<p>Sayori: "Of course, Yuri!"</p>
<p>(Sayori guides Yuri's hand to her bump, and she too feels the baby's kicks.)</p>
<p>Yuri: (in awe) "It's so surreal. To think that there's a life growing inside of you, Sayori."</p>
<p>Monika: "I can't believe I almost missed out on this. Mind if I join in too?"</p>
<p>Sayori: "Not at all, Monika!"</p>
<p>(Monika joins the group and feels the baby's kicks with a smile.)</p>
<p>Monika: "It's a beautiful feeling, Sayori. I'm so happy for you."</p>
<p>Sayori: "Thank you, Monika. Little Sky means the world to me."</p>
<p>Natsuki: "Sayori, you're going to be an amazing mom."</p>
<p>Yuri: "Indeed. Your love and care will undoubtedly shape Little Sky into a wonderful person."</p>
<p>Sayori: "You guys always know how to make me feel loved. I'm grateful to have you as my friends."</p>
<p>Monika: "And we're grateful to have you, Sayori. Now, let's sit down and start our club meeting, shall we?"</p>
<p>(The four friends gather around and begin their usual club activities, the joy of feeling Little Sky's kicks lingering in their hearts.)</p></div>

